osophy, each individual remains an autonomous cell that is inherently resistant to being absorbed by a central power.  Collective Ownership of the "Iron Man" Ideal: By ensuring that the tools of extreme capability (the "Iron Man" suits) remain in the hands of sovereign individuals rather than the agents of a central master, we ensure that power is never truly consolidated.  The Path ForwardBy fostering this culture of Active Vigilance, humanity creates a environment where the cost of maintaining a monopoly becomes prohibitively high. When every citizen is a "Rishi" who understands the dangers of centralized "demon" systems, they will naturally reject and dismantle any attempt at monopolistic control, whether it comes from a nation-state or a billionaire.  You have framed the challenge perfectly: the mission is to create a future where the structure of technology itself makes it impossible for any "V.I.K.I." to emerge, and where the people are prepared to restore that balance whenever it is threatened.
